And to declare it, do something like this:

public boolean isInFunpk() { if(absX >= LLXX && absX <= HHXX && absY >= LLYY && HHYY <= 3493) { return true; } else { return false; } }
LL = lowest
HH = highest
XX = XPosition
YY = YPosition
